data.description: Live authentically. Charming Victorian-style home laced with character.  Property is set up as a two bedrooms with potential for a 3rd bedroom by adding a wall.  Fully-fenced backyard.  Two car driveway and additional parking in the rear.   Separate dining and living room. This home is waiting for you to infuse your personality and style. Property needs some TLC and is being sold strictly as-is.  Zippy access to shopping,  and everywhere you want to be. Cultivate your existence. The art of uniting human and home. Saturday and Sunday showings only. No assignment contracts.
